Implemented `noscope-3ez.11` end-to-end with TDD and committed.

- Updated user-facing clap help in `src/cli.rs`:
  - Added concrete root examples via `after_help` (`run`, `mint`, `revoke`, `revoke --from-stdin`)
  - Clarified `--profile` semantics for both `run` and `mint` (explicit mutual exclusion with `--provider/--role/--ttl`)
  - Clarified `--log-format` scope (runtime events on stderr only, does not affect `--output`)
  - Removed internal rule-jargon from help text (e.g., removed `(NS-071)` and `NS-065` mention in help descriptions)

- Added dedicated tests in `src/cli.rs` for each bead rule:
  - `help_includes_concrete_usage_examples`
  - `profile_help_clarifies_flag_behavior`
  - `log_format_help_clarifies_scope_and_relationship_to_output`
  - `user_facing_help_avoids_internal_rule_jargon` (plus extra edge check for `mint --help`)

